'''連恩·約翰·尼森'''{{OBE}}（{{lang-en|Liam John Neeson}}，{{bd|1952年|6月7日||}}）是一位[[英國|英國]][[男演員|男演員]]，曾經入圍[[奧斯卡最佳男主角獎|奧斯卡最佳男主角獎]]。他最知名的電影演出是《[[辛德勒的名單|辛德勒的名單]]》，也曾經在《[[星際大戰|星際大戰]]》系列電影中演出。2008年，在《[[即刻救援|即刻救援]]》中飾演趕去救女兒的退休[[中央情報局|中央情報局]]（CIA）情報員再度走紅，自此出演了其續集以及一連串動作片，成為動作影星。

== 早年生活 ==
尼森出生於[[北愛爾蘭|北愛爾蘭]][[安特里姆郡|安特里姆郡]]的[[巴利梅納|巴利梅納]]的一個[[天主教|天主教]]家庭，為廚師凱瑟琳·“基蒂”·尼森和小學工友伯納德·“巴尼”·尼森的兒子。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tiscali.co.uk/entertainment/film/biographies/liam_neeson_biog.html |title=Liam Neeson Biography |website=Tiscali |access-date=18 April 2007 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070118084156/http://www.tiscali.co.uk/entertainment/film/biographies/liam_neeson_biog.html |archive-date=18 January 2007 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/local-national/liam-neeson-bloody-sunday-made-me-learn-my-history-14251304.html |title=Liam Neeson: Bloody Sunday made me learn my history |newspaper=[[The_Belfast_Telegraph|The Belfast Telegraph]] |date=1 April 2010 |access-date=9 May 2010 |archive-date=25 December 2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101225233012/http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/local-national/liam-neeson-bloody-sunday-made-me-learn-my-history-14251304.html |url-status=live }}: (Commentary;''"Hollywood superstar Liam Neeson has told how he grew up in a religious Catholic background untouched by the Troubles."'')</ref>他在四個兄弟姐妹中的排行第三，他有三個姐妹，名叫伊麗莎白、伯納黛特和羅莎琳。連恩這個名字是以當地的牧師命名的。<ref>{{cite magazine |title=Liam Neeson Puts the Kettle On |magazine=GQ |last=Mansfield |first=Stephanie |date=December 1993}}</ref>

== 个人生活 ==
1980年，連恩尼遜與奧斯卡影后[[海倫·米蘭|海倫·米蘭]]曾因合作電影《神劍》相戀 5 年，當時還曾經同居。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZmAYzweMuZA&ab_channel=B.C.%26Lowy |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-12-02 |archive-date=2021-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211002093837/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZmAYzweMuZA&ab_channel=B.C.%26Lowy |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1994年7月，尼遜與影星[[娜塔莎·李察遜|娜塔莎·李察遜]]結婚，育有兩名兒子Michael 和 Daniel。2009年3月19日，娜塔莎·李察遜在[[加拿大|加拿大]][[魁北克|魁北克]]因[[滑雪|滑雪]][[意外|意外]][[事故|事故]]导致头部重伤去世。

他居住于[[紐約州|紐約州]]东南部[[達奇斯縣_(紐約州)|達奇斯縣]]的Millbrook村。2004年8月他与妻子一起购买了他家周围附近16英亩的土地<ref name="NeesonHome">{{cite web|last=Blaney|first=Retta|authorlink=|coauthors=|title='Natasha Richardson and Liam Neeson house profile – house pictures, rare facts and info about Natasha Richardson and Liam Neeson home in Millbrook, New York'|publisher=BeliefNet|date=|url=http://www.celebritydetective.com/Celebrity_Homes_Natasha-Richardson-Liam-Neeson-New-York.html|accessdate=2011-11-08|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305062202/http://www.celebritydetective.com/Celebrity_Homes_Natasha-Richardson-Liam-Neeson-New-York.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url = http://www.esquire.com/features/liam-neeson-0311|first = Tom|last = Chiatella|newspaper = Esquire|pages = 106–113|title = The hard luck and beautiful life of Liam Neeson [2011-02-15 interview]|date = 2011-03|accessdate = 2011-04-15|archive-date = 2014-12-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141222011329/http://www.esquire.com/features/liam-neeson-0311|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

事业早年他[[烟瘾|烟瘾]]非常大，后来成功[[戒烟|戒烟]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ptcchallenge.com/2010/06/the-a-team/ |title=The A Team |publisher=PTC Challenge |date=2010-06-01 |accessdate=2010-06-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101127112227/http://ptcchallenge.com/2010/06/the-a-team/ |archivedate=2010-11-27 }}</ref>。2009年8月，他在[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]的节目《[[早安美國|早安美國]]》中表示他已经加入[[美国国籍|美国国籍]]<ref name="news.bbc.co.uk">{{Cite news | title = "Actor Neeson becomes US citizen" – BBC News 26 August 2009 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/northern_ireland/8223680.stm | date = 2009-08-26 | accessdate = 2010-01-05 | archive-date = 2021-05-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210510191042/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/northern_ireland/8223680.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

他自己是[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦足球俱乐部]]的球迷<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1167515/Grieving-Liam-Neeson-looks-downcast-leaves-The-Ivy-alone.html|title=Grieving Liam Neeson looks downcast as he leaves The Ivy alone|date=2009-04-06|work=Daily Mail|accessdate=2011-02-22|location=London|archive-date=2021-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223072732/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1167515/Grieving-Liam-Neeson-looks-downcast-leaves-The-Ivy-alone.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年3月，他被[[联合国儿童基金会|联合国儿童基金会]]任命为爱心大使。

2014年12月，他在宣傳電影《[[即刻救援3|即刻救援3]]》的活動中，主動表示自己將到台灣拍片，並表示：「我對台灣很好奇，尤其是與中國大陸的關係，我很想搞清楚這些政治問題。當然我也相信台灣一定很美。」<ref>[https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%A3%E6%81%A9%E5%B0%BC%E9%81%9C%E4%BB%A5%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E7%A8%B1%E5%91%BC%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3-%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B43%E6%9C%88%E4%BE%86%E5%8F%B0%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87-%E6%83%B3%E6%90%9E%E6%B8%85%E6%A5%9A%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82-221125371.html 連恩尼遜以國家稱呼台灣-明年3月來台拍片 想搞清楚台灣與中國的關係] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150210040610/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%A3%E6%81%A9%E5%B0%BC%E9%81%9C%E4%BB%A5%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E7%A8%B1%E5%91%BC%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3-%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B43%E6%9C%88%E4%BE%86%E5%8F%B0%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87-%E6%83%B3%E6%90%9E%E6%B8%85%E6%A5%9A%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82-221125371.html |date=2015-02-10 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://tw.celebrity.yahoo.com/news/%E6%B2%89%E9%BB%98-30%E6%97%A5%E9%96%8B%E6%8B%8D-%E8%9C%98%E8%9B%9B%E4%BA%BA-%E5%9C%B0%E8%A1%A8%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E8%80%81%E7%88%B8%E4%BE%86%E5%8F%B0%E4%BA%86%E5%97%8E-120209335.html;_ylt=A2oKslWuZdlUeXsAeSdw1gt |title=《沉默》30日開拍，蜘蛛人、地表最強老爸來台了嗎？ |access-date=2015-02-10 |archive-date=2019-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603054013/https://tw.celebrity.yahoo.com/news/%E6%B2%89%E9%BB%98-30%E6%97%A5%E9%96%8B%E6%8B%8D-%E8%9C%98%E8%9B%9B%E4%BA%BA-%E5%9C%B0%E8%A1%A8%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E8%80%81%E7%88%B8%E4%BE%86%E5%8F%B0%E4%BA%86%E5%97%8E-120209335.html;_ylt=A2oKslWuZdlUeXsAeSdw1gt |dead-url=no }}</ref>

